textAnnotations.description:
ARIZONA
MEMPHIS
THE BIG
MARCH MADNESS
MATCHUP HERE IN
TULSA A NASTY AND
BITTER RIVALRY WHERE
WE'VE SEEN THE
THROWING OF SHARP
ELBONS, HARD CHARGES
FULL-COURT PRESSES
BALL-HOGGING AND
CHEAP GHOTS...
WHO WILL WIN?
TEXAS
OAKLAND
MAYOR DEWEY BARTLETT
TULSA CITY COUNCIL
